<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-label">FAQ</div>
  <h1>Straight answers. <span>No fluff.</span></h1>
  <p class="page-sub">Everything you need to know before spending $1,000 with someone you just found online.</p>
</div>
<div class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-group">
    <div class="faq-group-label">About the Assessment</div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">What exactly happens during the assessment?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">We schedule a one-on-one interview — in person when possible, or by phone or video depending on your location. We ask questions about how your business operates day to day. What your team spends time on, what is frustrating, what is repetitive, and where things fall through the cracks. That conversation becomes the foundation for your report.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">What does the report include?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">A written breakdown of every automation opportunity we identified — organized by priority and impact. Each recommendation shows what the solution is, why it fits your specific operation, and what it is worth in time saved and dollars recovered per month. Plus 3-4 actionable solutions you can implement yourself immediately, and a long-term automation plan showing what is possible if you want to go further.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">How long does the report take to deliver?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">You will have it within one week of your assessment session.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">Do I have to buy anything after the assessment?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">No. The report is yours to keep regardless of what you decide. Some clients implement the recommendations on their own. Some hire us to build it. Some file the report and come back later. All three are fine.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">What if I am not ready to implement anything yet?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">That is exactly why the report exists. You will know what the opportunities are, what they are worth, and what it would take to act on them — so when the timing is right you are not starting from scratch.</div></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-group">
    <div class="faq-group-label">About AI & Technology</div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">Do I need to know anything about AI?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Nothing. You do not need to understand the technology. You just need to know your business — we handle the rest.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">Will AI replace my staff?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">No. The goal is to take the repetitive, time-consuming tasks off your team's plate so they can focus on the work that actually needs a person. We do not automate work that requires human judgment — if the relationship or expertise is the differentiator, we do not touch that touchpoint.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">How do you know the ROI numbers are accurate?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">The numbers are built from the specific information you give us during the interview and published performance data from the tools we recommend. They are conservative estimates based on your actual workflows and rates — not generic industry averages.</div></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-group">
    <div class="faq-group-label">About Kodiak Strategy</div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">Where are you located and do you work remotely?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">We are based in the Black Hills of South Dakota and serve businesses across SD, ND, MT, WY, MN, and NE. In-person assessments are available across the region. The entire process can also be done remotely.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">What kinds of businesses do you work with?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Owner-operated businesses across the Northern Plains — optometry clinics, dental practices, law firms, accounting firms, insurance agencies, roofing companies, HVAC businesses, real estate agencies, and restaurants. If your team does the same things over and over every day there is almost certainly an opportunity worth finding.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">What happens after the assessment if I want to move forward?</span><span class="faq-icon">+</span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">We schedule a strategy call to walk through the report together. We present fully customized implementation options and you decide which one is the best fit. Then we get to work.</div></div></div>
  </div>
